data.description: Charming all-brick home located conveniently in the heart of Evansville. This home offers a gated driveway, outdoor firepit, concrete patio and a huge fully, fenced-in back yard. As you walk into the home you will enter the large living room with large windows allowing ample sunlight. The newly updated kitchen includes new appliances and an adjacent main floor laundry area off of the back door. Down the hall are 3 bedrooms and the newly remodeled bathroom including a smart mirror. All new interior paint and carpet make this home move-in ready for its new owners.
